            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="po-pr__item">
            <h2 class="po-pr__subheading">
              <a class="po-pr__button" v-on:click="set_print_size('print-large')">
                Large
              </a>
            </h2>
            <div class="po-pr__text po-pr__text--l">
              <p>The only thing certain about today&#8217;s municipal elections in Chicago is that it will settle little to nothing. From the mayoral race to a score of aldermanic elections, few if any of the most contentious races will have an outright winner; they’ll be settled in an April runoff. But today’s election is the most important [&hellip;]</p>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </transition>
</div>


      </article>

